---
title: Asian-inspired Beef Tacos with crunchy peanuts and slaw
description: Crunch and colour are two things that can be found in abundance in these Asian-inspired tacos, thanks to carrots, cabbage and a scattering of peanuts. Lime zest adds flavour to the beef mince while chopped chilli gives a bit of a kick.
